I'm almost sure you don't know the old version
fancylogin 0.99.5 (unless you're Andreas
Krennmair or Jochen Landvoigt)

fancylogin 0.99.6 supports

- /etc/securetty
- /etc/usertty
- utmp/wtmp-logging
- syslog-logging
- logging to files
- fancy logins
